paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the molecular mechanisms of long QT syndrome type 2 (LQT2) caused by KCNH2 mutations, focusing on the trafficking deficiencies of Kv11.1 proteins. No specific KCNH2 variants with penetrance data were mentioned.

challenges: The paper did not provide specific KCNH2 variant data with penetrance information.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the general mechanisms of KCNH2 mutations in LQT2 without detailing specific variants or penetrance data.
